Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:18.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到这股心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:22.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上双眼用心去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:29.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,满溢的热气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:33.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:40.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那一日的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:43.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:49.70,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,苏醒的追忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,katharsis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:57.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,解放吧 将一切解放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:00.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着未来跑动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,名为青涩和你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,现在立刻就传达到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:09.29,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,强而有力地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:14.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,朝那倾洒而出的光芒 伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:21.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,So Just Light Bravest Destiny
